 MedReport AI Agent Workflow

1. User uploads X-ray, MRI, CT scan, or lab report.
2. AI Image Analysis Agent checks the medical image.
3. OCR Agent extracts text from reports.
4. Disease Prediction Agent identifies possible diseases or abnormalities.
5. Report Generation Agent creates a structured medical report.
6. Human Doctor/Radiologist reviews the generated report.
7. Final report is stored and shared.

## Agents Used
- Image Analysis Agent
- OCR Agent
- Disease Prediction Agent
- Report Generation Agent
- Validation Agent

